{
  "texts": [
    "In collaborative agents such as ChatDev [18] and MetaGPT [23], different agents may communicate with each other.",
    "In this process, the conversation history in a dialog is remembered in the agent memories.",
    "Each utterance generated by the agent is influenced by its memory.",
    "(2) Action via plan following.",
    "In this strategy, the agent takes actions following its pregenerated plans."
  ]
}